data.description: Built in 2019 this unique home offers 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. As you enter a long hall way in the entrance on your left you will find the first bedroom. An open concept with the Master in the back of the house away from all the bedrooms. In the kitchen you will find a big island with plenty of cabinet space and a walk in pantry. Did I mention one of the guest bedrooms has it's own full bathroom, I guess you can call it a junior suite. All appliances convey.
